node.text: My custom wreath by Lisa, the talented owner of @bibelotseasonalwreaths just arrived! I am so grateful to have found a place to live and I just want to cover it in love! What better way then to decorate with special handmade pieces! ❤️💕#supportsmallbusiness #supporteachother #shopsmall #iloveyoudoor

node.text:
✨Changing to a NEW ball of yarn - Crochet ✨⠀
⠀
Tutorial video showing you what to do when it’s time to switch yarn. Have you reached the end of the ball you’re working with?? Or maybe it’s time to change colors? This video will show you how to get it done! ⠀
⠀
Both the Double Crochet scarf project AND Single Crochet scarf project are shown in this video (in that order ☺️).

#kickingitwithemmeandkirsten @kirstenstorms @lionbrandyarn @cocoknits @muudliving #crochetersofinstagram

node.text: I was so busy celebrating Dakota today that I didn’t take any pictures! Luckily my mom got this beautiful pic! Dakota looks so grown up! 😭😭 How on earth is she 4 already?!? Four years ago today we were at the hospital crying with joy over this sweet soul’s entrance into the world. Our lives were forever changed! #thisisfour

node.text: Eeeeeeeeeee! I’m so excited for Dakota to wake up tomorrow for her birthday that I can’t sleep! 😍☺️ (If you’re ever looking for me I will be hiding with yarn in her princess tent!)
